### get all appointentTypes
GET http://127.0.0.1:5011/api/admins/id/appointmentTypes

### get one by appointmentType name
GET http://127.0.0.1:5011/api/admins/id/appointmentTypes/Consultation


### create one appointmentType  /// Check-up
POST http://localhost:5011/api/admins/id/appointmentTypes
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Consultation" 
}

### update one appointmentType by name
PUT http://localhost:5011/api/admins/id/appointmentTypes/Consultation
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "available":"false"
}

### delete one appointmentType by name
DELETE http://localhost:5011/api/admins/id/appointmentTypes/Consultation

